## Sir Vaughan Jones

This article is dedicated to the mathematician. For the Welsh footballer, you’d have to look elsewhere, perhaps under [Vaughan Jones (footballer)](/Vaughan_Jones_(footballer)). Not that I see the appeal, but people have their… preferences.

